  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to investigate the effects of the impairment-specific and
      augmented intervention based balance and strength training on turning performance in
      individuals with chronic stroke.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
